metadata.name: Randomness
metadata.description:
This is a unique NFT from the Revelation collection. 

5000x3751

Personality is formed during critical difficult periods, where you can't just go with the flow. Accidents provoke such situations. They can bring new emotions and reveal key features of your spirit.

There's nothing left to do but accept the existence of man and randomness in the same field and inevitability of their meeting and enjoy the randomness!
